QSP Agent Debian package
========================

Installed paths:

- Binary: /usr/bin/qsp-agent
- Configuration: /etc/qsp-agent/config.toml
- Systemd unit: /lib/systemd/system/qsp-agent.service
- Man page: /usr/share/man/man1/qsp-agent.1.gz

The package installs a dedicated `qsp-agent` system user and group.

The service runs in the foreground under systemd. Do not enable the `--daemon`
flag in the service definition.

If the radio device is exposed through `/dev/tty*` or `/dev/serial/*`, the
`qsp-agent` user may need to be added to a device access group such as
`dialout`.
